<author><name><![CDATA[lidnariq]]></name></author>
<updated>2015-03-01T01:11:14-07:00</updated>
<published>2015-03-01T01:11:14-07:00</published>
<id>http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12436&amp;p=142263#p142263</id>
<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12436&amp;p=142263#p142263"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Trying to get FME-7 IRQs right]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12436&amp;p=142263#p142263"><![CDATA[
Correct behavior: All writes to register &quot;D&quot; (i.e. writing to $Axxx after $0D has been written to $8xxx) should acknowledge the IRQ, regardless of the value written. Writes to registers &quot;E&quot; and &quot;F&quot; shouldn't.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3512">lidnariq</a> — Sun Mar 01, 2015 1:11 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
