<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12436&amp;p=142251#p142251"><![CDATA[
clarification for posterity: Mednafen's debugging console is 640x480, (at least in NES mode, haven't tried others). x2 scaling for NES on default settings (top/bottom 8 scanlines hidden) is 512x448.<br /><br />Thus, (2.5, 2) scaling minimum with all scanlines displayed.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6603">Myask</a> — Sat Feb 28, 2015 8:56 pm</p><hr />
